[[todo list entry guide]]

[name] {(prio) 0-4} entry (claryfication if needed)
0 = very high (absolutely needs done before next release)
1 = high      (ideally before next release)
2 = medium    (target for future release)
3 = low       (consider for future release)
4 = very low  (add sometime)
not binding besides prio 0, just suggestions

